psquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#f9f9f9;color:#2d3134;font-size:15px;\u0022\u003EIts formatted with the 24 hour clock then month day year so: 031309052022 means 313am on september 5th 2022. Its a far more accurate way of tracking when something is posted. The default time stamp used by the forum becomes less accurate as time passes.\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#f9f9f9;color:#2d3134;font-size:15px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 style=\u0022border-style:none;vertical-align:middle;\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superluminal Gremlin","CreatedById":221533,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-11-03T01:33:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nahhhhhhh\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AlamoVampire","CreatedById":78020,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-11-03T01:40:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/221533-superluminal-gremlin/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022221533\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/221533-superluminal-gremlin/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Superluminal Gremlin\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0i hope my explanation as delivered by \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/221143-rutabaga22/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022221143\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/221143-rutabaga22/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Rutabaga22\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0(thank you for the assist kind soul) was helpful \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E204011022022\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ColdJ","CreatedById":211123,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-11-03T04:12:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs people asking, what \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/78020-alamovampire/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002278020\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/78020-alamovampire/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@AlamoVampire\u003C/a\u003Es time stamp is, one of the most asked questions on the forum? \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AlamoVampire","CreatedById":78020,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-11-03T05:39:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224194661\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221667448734\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022211123\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ColdJ\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, ColdJ said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs people asking, what \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/78020-alamovampire/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002278020\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/78020-alamovampire/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@AlamoVampire\u003C/a\u003Es time stamp is, one of the most asked questions on the forum? \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIve seen it asked quite a number of times (id hesitate to guess, but its asked alot) since i started doing it in 2016. Its why ive asked at one point if it should be added to an faq somewhere \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u00A0im always happy to explain it, but i take equal joy watching the speculation that pops up about it from time to time.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E003911032022\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-11-03T09:53:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224194362\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221667408075\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002278020\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022AlamoVampire\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n16 hours ago, AlamoVampire said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf a user makes a name change request and then logs out, I would imagine a certain amount of panic if they try to log in unaware the change took place and bounced off the authentication during log in.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs a user who changed his name, I can attest to this exact thing happening 100% of the time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAt least 100% of the time I did it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AlamoVampire","CreatedById":78020,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-11-03T10:37:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUsing \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/73725-superfluous-j/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002273725\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/73725-superfluous-j/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Superfluous J\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0as an example of what I was thinking, specifically in the portion he quoted and confirmed as what happened to him, would it be possible for whomever maintains the actual under the hood workings of our lovely forum to possibly add in a way for users who request a name change and are logged out of the forum to receive an email alerting them that their requested new name is active? Or is this just wishful thinking on my part?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n053711032022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-11-03T10:58:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224194728\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221667471849\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002278020\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022AlamoVampire\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n19 minutes ago, AlamoVampire said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUsing \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/73725-superfluous-j/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002273725\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/73725-superfluous-j/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Superfluous J\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0as an example of what I was thinking, specifically in the portion he quoted and confirmed as what happened to him, would it be possible for whomever maintains the actual under the hood workings of our lovely forum to possibly add in a way for users who request a name change and are logged out of the forum to receive an email alerting them that their requested new name is active? Or is this just wishful thinking on my part?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s unfortunately wishful thinking. Invision (who make the software we use) seem to be more interested in adding internet points systems and badges than actually useful features.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-11-03T12:38:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224194728\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221667471849\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002278020\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022AlamoVampire\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, AlamoVampire said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUsing \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/73725-superfluous-j/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002273725\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/73725-superfluous-j/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Superfluous J\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0as an example of what I was thinking, specifically in the portion he quoted and confirmed as what happened to him, would it be possible for whomever maintains the actual under the hood workings of our lovely forum to possibly add in a way for users who request a name change and are logged out of the forum to receive an email alerting them that their requested new name is active? Or is this just wishful thinking on my part?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022tel:053711032022\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E053711032022\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe have a much longer list of higher priority items than something that will happen only once to a user and only when they request it to happen. \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-11-03T13:13:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224194728\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221667471849\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002278020\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022AlamoVampire\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, AlamoVampire said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUsing \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/73725-superfluous-j/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002273725\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/73725-superfluous-j/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Superfluous J\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0as an example of what I was thinking, specifically in the portion he quoted and confirmed as what happened to him, would it be possible for whomever maintains the actual under the hood workings of our lovely forum to possibly add in a way for users who request a name change and are logged out of the forum to receive an email alerting them that their requested new name is active? Or is this just wishful thinking on my part?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n053711032022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf this does happen to you, and you change your name and unwittingly cannot log into the forum because of the name change, you can use the \u0022forgot my username\u0022 option. I know this from \u003Cem\u003Eexperience\u003C/em\u003E, the great teacher of all things. There are two other forums I use that also use this same software (Invision). One allows the user to change their own name, the other follows similar protocols as we do here. And that\u0027s the one where I had no notification the user name had changed (from the old one - alanaeas to adsii1970).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nWhen you log in, simply click the link that says \u0022forgot user name/password\u0022 and it takes you to a screen where you must enter the email address you used when you first created your original account. Enter the password, click submit.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nCheck that email. It will contain your user name and a link to reset your password. If you need to reset your password, then do so.\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#c0392b;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EIf you do not need to reset your password and just needed to find out if your user name was changed, then go to step 3.\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffff00;\u0022\u003EIf you need to reset your password, follow the instructions contained within the forum software. It is literally step-by-step instructions. \u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nGo to the forum login screen, enter the shown user name and your password. You\u0027re back in. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0 \u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224194775\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221667479112\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n43 minutes ago, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe have a much longer list of higher priority items than something that will happen only once to a user and only when they request it to happen. \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/64714-gargamel/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002264714\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/64714-gargamel/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Gargamel\u003C/a\u003E is correct in this. None of the moderation team are paid; we are all volunteers. Right now, my life has been completely turned upside down, shaken up, and then dropped on the floor. What began as an easy semester with three undergraduate classes at a local community college, two graduate classes at a local university, and 25 advisees (students who I advise on their academic endeavors) has turned into a living nightmare. I now am advising 37 students and have picked up an additional graduate course in U.S. Constitutional History since the tenured professor quit in the middle of the term. I am now averaging about 60 to 70\u00A0 hours a week working in my vocation.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe time I have on the forum has gone from about five hours each day to maybe an hour and a half - if I am lucky. Last week I was only able to get on the forum for a total of 3 hours for the entire week. While I cannot speak for other members of the moderation team, I place my focus on the things that are the most important for the community. Not too long ago, in this very thread, someone commented about the lack of spam and spambots - and we do not use any automated process but the human process. We operate as a team, we discuss what we do. We need a balanced approach and we are all passionate about our love for the forum community and our service given to it. Consider us the forum equivalent of the Vatican\u0027s Swiss Guard - except y\u0027all are who we serve, we protect the integrity of the forum, and we don\u0027t get paid (wait, does that mean that \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/218794-ghostii_space/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022218794\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/218794-ghostii_space/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Ghostii_Space\u003C/a\u003E is the commandant of the Forum guard?).\u00A0 \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022giphy.gif\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022 src=\u0022https://media.giphy.com/media/deR32LdMuvIfZDheOL/giphy.gif\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rutabaga22","CreatedById":221143,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-11-04T01:31:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat are the rules for posts on my profile? Does it have to be ksp related or could I share something I\u0027m proud of in another game?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-11-04T01:37:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224195029\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221667525466\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022221143\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Rutabaga22\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, Rutabaga22 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat are the rules for posts on my profile? Does it have to be ksp related or could I share something I\u0027m proud of in another game?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs long as they stick to the \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/guidelines/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003ECommunity Guidelines\u003C/a\u003E, it should be fine.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-11-04T09:03:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI just wanted to say that, even though it\u0027s not possible at the moment, your suggestion, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/78020-alamovampire/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002278020\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/78020-alamovampire/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@AlamoVampire\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0was a really good one, and it\u0027s great that you care so much about other people! Empathy is a beautiful quality.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-11-06T12:36:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTo be 100% clear, I was not complaining. I was admitting.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-11-06T16:07:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224196045\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221667738173\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\