11158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221667750864\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n31 minutes ago, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u2019m still complaining about your name change\u2026..\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, I admit that I also miss the Fifth Horseman!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-11-11T22:15:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224197854\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221668198962\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022223493\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Laikanaut\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Laikanaut said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf we want to discuss a mod idea for KSP 2, which is the appropriate forum? I\u0027m unsure if the \u0022add on discussions\u0022 area is designated for KSP only\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s as good a spot as any until there are appropriate subs for KSP2.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-11-11T23:16:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224195029\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221667525466\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022221143\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Rutabaga22\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 11/3/2022 at 8:31 PM, Rutabaga22 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat are the rules for posts on my profile? Does it have to be ksp related or could I share something I\u0027m proud of in another game?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are a variety of threads already in existence on the forum that are about other games, too. The one that comes to mind is:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022207831\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed8593295270\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/206231-whats-your-favorite-game-except-kerbal-space-program/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:150px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s a place where folks share all kinds of stuff about the games they play, including strategies and screen shots. Might be something to take a look into.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ShuttlePilot","CreatedById":209278,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-11-17T16:04:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat if a user intentonally annoys a moderator, what are the consequences?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-11-17T16:04:40Z\u0022 title=\u002211/17/2022 04:04  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003ENovember 17, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by ShuttlePilot\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}